high_descs: turn right and walk over to the right side of the toilet on the left
grab a candle off of the bath tub ledge on your right up ahead
move to the left a bit and face the toilet again
place the candle down on top of the back side of the toilet
turn around and walk over to the bath tub ledge on your left, turn to face it
grab the candle off of the bath tub ledge there
turn left and walk back over to the toilet again
place the candle on top of the back side of the toilet
anns.task_desc: place two candles down on top of the toilet

high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the tub, then turn left to face the toilet.
Pick up the candle off of the toilet.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right to face the toilet.
Put the candle on top of the toilet tank in front of the rightmost spray bottle.
Turn around and walk up to the sink, then turn left and walk up to the tub.
Pick up the candle off of the tub.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and walk up to the toilet.
Put the candle on top of the toilet tank to the left of the candle that's already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two candles to the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the tub.
Pick up the candle on the side of the tub near the toilet.
Turn to face the toilet.
Place the candle on the toilet tank in front of the rightmost spray bottle.
Turn right and walk the other end of the tub.
Pick up the candle on the lip of the tub.
Turn left and walk back to the toilet.
Place the candle on the toilet tank, to the left of the first candle.
anns.task_desc: Place two candles on a toilet tank.
